{
  "stem": "8072.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My dad, you know, had a beard, so they tried to take all eligible male-- you know they're afraid-- put in camps and things like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my dad didn't go out of the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My two brothers-- one of them was in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of them had run away from home because the Germans came close-- I don't know where he was running.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and I had to start-- if we had to go someplace, I was the one that was going.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, like we had found out by the third or the fourth day, that a camp nearby that was basically like a holding camp where they had a lot of people-- Jewish people-- from our town, our hometown.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so some of the people from our hometown wanted to go to visit them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was about 15 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's a long way to walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And since we had a horse and wagon, we took about-- I don't know how many people-- a couple more people in from the town, where they had transportation.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we went to take these people to their town with some bread and things like that, and to see if any of your relatives are there, or any of your family.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And also give them some food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I was there, I found out that my brother was-- had-- was in that camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I gave him some food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And also, at that time, there was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You had to be in by a certain-- 6 o'clock, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1939, right when the Germans occupied Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just like-- it wasn't existing very long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just like maybe a holding camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
